  <h2>The Range of Scope</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Visual check.</strong> A look at an accessible, already-open tank.</li>
    <li><strong>Locating and opening.</strong> Finding the tank and opening the lids.</li>
    <li><strong>Fuller evaluation.</strong> Pumping, flow testing and component checks.</li>
    <li><strong>Documentation.</strong> A written record of findings.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Ask Before You Compare</h2>
  <p>
    Because scope varies, ask what a given inspection includes before comparing prices — a visual check and a full evaluation are different services. To arrange one, <a href="/septic-inspection-cookeville-tn/">see inspections</a> or <a href="/request-service/">request septic service</a>.
  </p>

